mid_count: Count of the number of MIDS in the dyad-year, both total and new MIDs
mid_ongoing_m: Main MID ongoing but did not start that year (relevant for multi-year MIDS)
onset_other: Dyad members had another MID (not just main MID) start that year
ongoing_other: Dyad members had another MID (not just main MID) ongoing that year
main_disno: Number of the MID identified as the key MID in that year
strtday_m: Start Day of the dyad's key MID
strtmnth_m: Start Month of the dyad's key MID
strtyr_m: Start Year of the dyad's key MID
endday_m: End Day of the dyad's key MID
endmnth_m: End Month of the dyad's key MID
endyear_m: End Year of the dyad's key MID
outcome_m: Outcome of the dyad's key MID, 9 point scale
settlmnt_m: Settlement type of the dyad's key MID, 5 point scale
fatlev_m: Fatality level of the dyad's key MID, 7 point scale
highact_m: Highest military confrontation action of the dyad's key MID, 24 point scale
hihost_m: Highest level of hostility of the dyad's key MID, 5 point scale
recip_m: Initiator of MID can NOT be clearly identified in the dyad's key MID, Yes or No
nosideA_m: Number of states on side A of the dyad's key MID
nosideB_m: Number of states on side B of the dyad's key MID
sideaa_m: State A on the side that initiated the dyad's key MID, 1 = Yes
revstata_m: State A revisitionist in the dyad's key MID, 1=yes
revtypea_m: Type of revision sought by state A of the dyad's key MID (if revisionist), 5 point scale
fatleva_m: Level of fatality incurred by State A of the dyad's key MID, see FATLEV
highmcaa_m: Highest military confrontration action of State A in the dyad's key MID, see HIGHACT
hihosta_m: Highest level of hostility reached by State A of the dyad's key MID, see HIHOST
orignata_m: State A is an original participant in the dyad's key MID, 1 = Yes
sideab_m: State B on Initator's side of the dyad's key MID, 1=Yes
revstatb_m: State B revisitionist in the dyad's key MID, 1=yes
revtypeb_m: Type of revision sought by state B of the dyad's key MID (if revisionist), 5 point scale
fatlevb_m: Level of fatality incurred by State B of the dyad's key MID, see FATLEV
highmcab_m: Highest military confrontration action of State B in the dyad's key MID, see HIGHACT
hihostb_m: Highest level of hostility reached by State B of the dyad's key MID, see HIHOST
orignatb_m: State B is an original participant in the dyad's key MID, 1 = Yes
rolea_m: Role of Stata A in the dyad's key MID, 1 or 2 = initator side; 3 or 4 = target side
roleb_m: Role of Stata B in the dyad's key MID, 1 or 2 = initator side; 3 or 4 = target side
dyad_rolea_m: Role of State A in just the dyadic portion of the dyad's key MID, 1 or 2 = initator side; 3 or 4 = target side
dyad_roleb_m: Role of State A in just the dyadic portion of the dyad's key MID, 1 or 2 = initator side; 3 or 4 = target side
war_m: Does the dyad's key MID rise to the level of a COW War in that year, 1=Yes
durindx_m: Duration year of the dyad's key MID, i.e. 1 or 2 or 3, etc.
duration_m: Number of dispute days of dyad's key MID in that year
cumdurat_m: Cumulative number of days of the dyad's key MID in that year
mid5hiact_m: MID data 5.01 Highest military confrontration action of the dyad's key MID
mid5hiacta_m: MID data 5.01 Highest military confrontration action of State A in the dyad's key MID
mid5hiactb_m: MID data 5.01 Highest military confrontration action of State B in the dyad's key MID
severity_m: Highest severity action of the dyad's key MID, ranges from 0 to 100
severitya_m: Highest severity score committed by State A of the dyad's key MID, ranges from 0 to 100
severityb_m: Highest severity score committed by State B of the dyad's key MID, ranges from 0 to 100
ongo2014_m: The dyad's key MID is an ongoing MID in 2014
new_m: The dyad's key MID is a new dyadic MID in Year
